name: sample

prompt_map.0: Envision a stained glass style artwork of an girl, where the intricate beauty and vibrant colors of stained glass windows are masterfully depicted. The girl is transformed through a mosaic of colored glass pieces, each contributing to a detailed and harmonious composition. Light plays a crucial role, giving life to the colors and creating a luminous, ethereal effect. The design may include traditional stained glass motifs such as floral patterns, geometric shapes, or religious symbols, depending on the context. This style is about more than artistic representation; it’s a celebration of the historic and artistic significance of stained glass, where the girl becomes a part of a grander narrative. Its depiction in stained glass style elevates it to a work of art, imbued with the elegance and spirituality that this medium has represented for centuries.
